&lt;p&gt;Home Oxygen Service Secretary - Part Time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;19 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a part time medical secretaryon a fixed term contract for 6 months to our busy and friendly Home Oxygen Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a team player who is able to manage their own workload but also prioritise changing workloads working independently. The successful candidate will carry out a comprehensive range of administrative and secretarial support to the Specialist Nurses. Sound knowledge in hospital IT systems and&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you possess excellent communication skills and have sound experience in medical typing, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Feel free to contact us if you would like an informal visit or phone conversation. Any of the team would be delighted to speak to you.&lt;/p&gt;
